Nostalgia?

43
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,870
Baru je buat hari tu...

44
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:32,630
Ah. Oh ya, ya.

45
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:35,050
Siot ah. Terlepas pula dari mulut.

46
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:37,450
Jomlah, kita belajar betul-betul.

47
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,530
Kamu kan ada impian.

48
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:40,970
Impian?

49
00:02:41,510 --> 00:02:43,579
Aku ni, ada impian ke?

50
00:02:46,770 --> 00:02:48,110
Yosh. Saya dah buat keputusan.

51
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:48,980
Huh?

52
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,030
Hina yang akan ajar kamu.

53
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:57,900
Wooaah!!!

54
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,180
Asal?

55
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:03,130
Ini pertama kali aku masuk
ke dalam bilik perempuan.

56
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:05,760
Janganlah tengok sangat.

57
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,880
Maaflah.

58
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,960
Pertimbangan rasa memang takde ke...

59
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,250
Maaflah, ya.

60
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:13,550
Tak sangka kamu nak datang,
saya tak dapat nak sediakan apa-apa.

61
00:03:13,650 --> 00:03:17,150
Walaupun ni, pertama kali Hina
bawa budak lelaki ke sini.

62
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,040
Mama!

63
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,260
Okey je. Tak perlu ambil kisah.

64
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,400
Comel lah budak ni.

65
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,540
Sejak bila korang rapat ni?

66
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:23,470
Kelas sama ke?

67
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,770
Dah. Dahlah tu, mama. Keluarlah.

68
00:03:25,770 --> 00:03:26,820
Alaaa...

69
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:27,920
Teman lelaki ke?

70
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,790
Mama!

71
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,170
Tak faham langsunglah.

72
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:36,230
Oh ya, terima kasih tau, sebab tolong adik saya.

73
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:36,990
Oh?

74
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:40,180
Kamu tolong dia waktu dia kena
buli dengan geng delinkuen lain.

75
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:41,250
Aah.

76
00:03:41,250 --> 00:03:42,490
Papa kami,

77
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:45,280
sangat sibuk sampai jarang balik ke rumah.

78
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:48,230
Naoto, walaupun dia benci dengan papa,

79
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,550
baru ni, tiba-tiba dia cakap dia nak jadi macam papa.

80
00:03:51,550 --> 00:03:52,360
Huh?

81
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:56,540
Papa, pegawai polis.

82
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:57,360
Ouh.

83
00:03:57,910 --> 00:04:00,310
Sebab tulah, Naoto jadi pegawai polis.

84
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:00,900
Eh?

85
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,610
Dia belum jadi lagilah.

86
00:04:02,610 --> 00:04:03,670
Sekarang memang mustahil lah.

87
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:05,300
Y-Y-Y-Ye lah kan.

88
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,480
Apa yang aku merepek ni?

89
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,570
Tapi kan...

90
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:12,200
yang dibantunya rasanya aku.

91
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:13,090
Eh?

92
00:04:13,390 --> 00:04:14,410
Dia tu...

93
00:04:14,410 --> 00:04:16,329
boleh menjadi pegawai polis yang bagus.

94
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:20,380
Walaupun dia akan menjadi
pegawai yang tak rileks sikit.

95
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:23,220
Takemichi, kamu dah berubahlah.

96
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:25,080
Y-Y-Ye ke?

97
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,620
Kat mana?

98
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:27,810
Hmm...

99
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:30,590
Kamu macam dah menjadi lebih baik...

100
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,600
dah menjadi lebih matang...

101
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:36,080
Rasa macam bersembang
dengan orang dewasa.

102
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,250
Eh??

103
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,180
Tajam betul lah dia.

104
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,260
Aku ni 12 tahu lebiih tua.

105
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:43,990
Mungkin yang tu kut sebahagian
Takemichi yang Hina tak tahu.

106
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:44,750
Eh?

107
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:49,490
Saya nak tahu lebihlah pasal Takemichi.

108
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,220
Ehh??! Bunga apilah!

109
00:04:57,220 --> 00:05:00,270
Oh haahlah. Hari ni persembahan bunga api.

110
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:06,810
Weh, jomlah kita pergi ke atas bumbung.

111
00:05:09,470 --> 00:05:12,660
Wah, cantiknya.

112
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,840
Cepatlah, Takemichi.

113
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,800
Siotlah.

114
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,230
Seronoknya.

115
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:25,360
Kehidupan aku sebelum ni, takde pun macam tu.

116
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,930
Bentuk hati?

117
00:05:28,930 --> 00:05:30,900
Weh, kamu tengok tak yang tadi.

118
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,750
Aku nak berada di sini buat selamanya.

119
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,970
Aku tak kembali ke masa depan.

120
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:38,050
Masa depan kan...

121
00:05:38,050 --> 00:05:39,680
Hina...

122
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,780
dah takde.

123
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:46,350
Okey je kut, kalau pegang tangan.

124
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,640
Panas.

125
00:05:59,850 --> 00:06:01,380
Hina...

126
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,580
Apa?

127
00:06:05,130 --> 00:06:06,980
T-Terima kasih.

128
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:08,750
Naoto?

129
00:06:10,170 --> 00:06:12,050
Kalau kau bersalam dengan aku, tulah pencetusnya.

130
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:16,760
N-Naoto!

131
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,840
Eh? Naoto, kamu pun datang juga?

132
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,610
Ya.

133
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:23,520
Aduh, siotlah!!

134
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:27,880
Takemichi.

135
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,520
Aku dah kembali semula.

136
00:06:30,850 --> 00:06:33,690
Maksudnya, kau dah
berjaya kembali ke masa silam.

137
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,340
Dah agak dah bersalam, tulah pencetusnya.

138
00:06:36,450 --> 00:06:39,870
Kenapa kau ada kat situ?

139
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:40,290
Eh?

140
00:06:40,290 --> 00:06:41,770
Apa yang kau cakap ni?

141
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:46,180
Tak kisahlah, teori aku memang tak salah.

142
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:48,150
Ya. Yalah.

143
00:06:48,150 --> 00:06:49,990
Dan kau telah kembali ke sini.

144
00:06:49,990 --> 00:06:50,990
Eh?

145
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,880
Aku dah faham.

146
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,200
Semuanya.

147
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:58,580
Kau dah kembali, maksudnya
dah ada perkembangan kan?

148
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:00,980
Eh? Umm...

149
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:04,150
Kau tersilap pegang tangan aku?!

150
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:06,020
Fokus betul-betul lah.

151
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:10,070
Ada benda yang kau faham tentang
perentasan masa yang kali kedua ni.

152
00:07:10,730 --> 00:07:11,510
Ouh?

153
00:07:12,710 --> 00:07:14,480
Kebolehan merentas masa kau tu...

154
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:17,750
kau akan kembali ke 12 tahun yang
lepas pada hari yang sama.

155
00:07:18,530 --> 00:07:21,500
Contohnya, kalau kau kembali
ke zaman silam hari ni,

156
00:07:21,650 --> 00:07:26,660
Kalau kau berada seminggu di zaman silam,

157
00:07:26,990 --> 00:07:29,940
dan pada masa sekarang pun
seminggu akan berlalu juga.

158
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:32,890
Dan bila kau kembali ke zaman silam,

159
00:07:33,030 --> 00:07:34,430
badan kau,

160
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,190
menjadi kaku, seperti ketiadaan roh.

161
00:07:36,409 --> 00:07:38,590
Maksudnya aku mati ke?

162
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:42,560
Hanya badan kau saja yang
berada di masa sekarang.

163
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,500
Owh, sebab aku menjadi kaku.

164
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:48,890
Ni agak bahaya, kalau kau nak merentas masa,

165
00:07:48,890 --> 00:07:50,320
kita akan buatnya dalam bilik aku.

166
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,409
Jadi...

167
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:54,800
Apa dah jadi misi kau yang ingin menghalang
perjumpaan antara Kisaki dan Sano?

168
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,330
Um...

169
00:07:56,770 --> 00:07:58,570
Aku dah jumpa dengan Mikey.

170
00:07:58,570 --> 00:07:59,590
Mikey?

171
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:01,400
Ouh. Sano kan.

172
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:02,950
Dengar ni, Mikey.

173
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:05,420
Walaupun Mikey delinkuen, dia tu baiklah.

174
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,260
Huh?

175
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:08,500
Kenapa kau tak bunuh dia?

176
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,070
Eh?

177
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:09,870
Bunuh?

178
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:12,390
Orang yang bunuh kak aku tu "orang baik"?

179
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:14,160
Kau dah tertipu dengannya di masa silam ke?

180
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,810
Bukanlah.

181
00:08:14,810 --> 00:08:15,660
Dengar sini.

182
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:17,140
Mikey tu sekarang,

183
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:21,240
melakukan jenayah yang polis sendiri
pun tak dapat menghalangnya.

184
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:22,780
Sebolehnya,

185
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,980
aku nak bunuh dia dengan tangan aku sendiri.

186
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:35,679
Naoto.

187
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:37,760
Jom kita berjumpa dengan Mikey.

188
00:08:38,409 --> 00:08:39,179
Bahayalah.

189
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:42,409
Aku nak berjumpa dengannya
dan tanya terus kepadanya.

190
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:44,700
Apa yang kau nak tanya, tak ada maknanya lah.

191
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:47,670
Mikey, adalah orang yang boleh dipercayai.

192
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:52,440
Aku dengar sendiri daripada Mikey,
kenapa Toman dah berubah.

193
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,080
Sebelum kembali ke masa silam,

194
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,060
Ada benda yang aku nak pastikan dulu.

195
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:01,440
Jom ikut aku mencari Mikey.

196
00:09:02,090 --> 00:09:03,300
Tolonglah, Naoto.

197
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:11,170
Aku tak tahu apa yang dah terjadi kat masa silam.

198
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,260
Kau memang dah berubahlah, Takemichi.

199
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,160
Eh?

200
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,600
Ye ke?

201
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:16,800
Kat mana yang aku berubah?

202
00:09:17,350 --> 00:09:19,200
Kau dah tak lemah dah.

203
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,620
Sikit je kut aku rasa.

204
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,910
Maksudnya, aku dah menjadi lebih bergaya sikit ke?

205
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:27,440
Okey, mari kita cari macam
mana nak berjumpa dengan Mikey.

206
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:30,040
Weh, weh, maksudnya aku ni dah lebih matang kan.

207
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:31,250
Weh, weh.

208
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,640
Takyah nak berhidung tinggi sangatlah.

209
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:34,740
Takemichi, kau susunkan dokumen-dokumen tu.

210
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,340
Bahaya betul lah, Geng Manji Tokyo ni.

211
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:43,290
Mikey tu meman betul-betul berjaga-jaga.

212
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,490
Polis pun tak dapat menjejakinya.

213
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:49,850
Telefon bimbitnya pun mungkin
kontrak langganan dengan nama palsu.

214
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,470
Siapa ni?

215
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:53,160
Hmm?

216
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:59,400
Ahli hebat Toman, Atsushi Sendou...

217
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:00,930
Akkun lah.

218
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:04,020
Akkun?

219
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,190
Kawan Takemichi?

220
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:06,970
Urm.

221
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,150
Peliklah.

222
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,560
Dia tu masa dia umur 16 tahun,

223
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:14,620
dia ditahan oleh polis kerana
menikam Masataka Kiyomizu.

224
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:18,440
Dia tu sepatutnya delinkuen bawahan je.

225
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:22,820
Aku memang nak tikam Kiyomasa tadi.

226
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:25,120
Oh ya, dia ada sebut pasal tu.

227
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:26,550
Entah-entah...

228
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,530
Masa silam sudah berubah?!

229
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:31,830
Akkun tak ditahan oleh polis,

230
00:10:32,010 --> 00:10:33,800
sebab dia tak tikam Kiyomasa.

231
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:36,100
Takemichi dah menjadi rapat dengan Mikey,

232
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:37,850
mungkin Sendou pun...

233
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:40,590
Akkun dah menjadi orang atasan Toman...

234
00:10:43,250 --> 00:10:43,900
Oh ya.

235
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:45,850
Kau boleh ke hubungi dengan Sendou?

236
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:46,400
Eh...

237
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,570
Hah.

238
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,650
Kalau nombor dia tak berubah.

239
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:54,050
Kalau Atsushi Sendou dah menjadi
orang atasan, kita hubungi Mikey melalui dia.

240
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,710
Ouh?!

241
00:10:58,230 --> 00:11:00,220
Dalam kotor tau, jadi siap sedia jelah.

242
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,830
Rasanya, aku dah boleh nampak kut.

243
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,440
Ew, bapak ah gelinya.

244
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,570
